Speaker 2: Yeah, it sure is. I love this time of year in New England.

Speaker 2: Absolutely! I've been enjoying the extra daylight for studying.

Speaker 1: Don't worry, you will. And remember, the journey is just as important as the destination.
Speaker 2: That's true. I'm learning a lot and it's really exciting.
Speaker 1: That's the spirit! Hey, if you ever need any advice on finance, feel free to ask. I'll be glad to help.
Speaker 2: Thank you, I appreciate that. I might take you up on that offer!
Speaker 1: Anytime. Well, I'd better be off. Have a great day of studying!
Speaker 2: Thanks! Have a great day at work too.
